Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.89,0:02:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀 有失远迎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.30,0:02:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位爷爷就是研究组的主任
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.68,0:02:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堤内老师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.48,0:02:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我见过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.96,0:02:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那时救我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.98,0:02:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.05,0:02:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是研究所
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在研制阻止能力发作的疫苗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.64,0:02:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疫苗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.78,0:02:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们得病了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.54,0:02:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.57,0:02:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特殊能力是一种病
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.37,0:02:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须在下一波粒子到来前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.94,0:02:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给全世界的人注射疫苗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.03,0:02:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粒子？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.43,0:02:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道长周期彗星「夏洛特」吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.14,0:02:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我知道的说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.74,0:02:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 小朋友你很喜欢星星吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.26,0:02:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的！我爱天文观测的说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.59,0:02:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏洛特彗星每隔75年飞近地球一次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.40,0:02:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞近时 会有未知的粒子洒在地球上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.08,0:03:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而吸入粒子的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.17,0:03:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会在敏感的年纪里获得特别的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.48,0:03:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为深入脑神经的粒子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.35,0:03:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会唤醒沉睡的大脑领域
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.60,0:03:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是…能力的来源吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.79,0:03:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大约四百年前 这颗彗星十分接近地球时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.71,0:03:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就洒下了无数粒子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.73,0:03:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时 有许多吸入粒子的欧洲人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.85,0:03:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成了身具异能的女巫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.60,0:03:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕能力的人们开始猎巫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.89,0:03:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数以万计的能力者惨遭虐杀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.40,0:03:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十二年前 彗星再一次掠过大气层
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.13,0:03:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身怀特殊能力的年轻人接连出现
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.36,0:03:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有宇 说的就是我们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.81,0:03:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了今后不再发生这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.22,0:03:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在研制疫苗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.04,0:03:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在日本已经投入生产
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.93,0:03:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来可以放心了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.38,0:04:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 只有我能管到的日本还算安全
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.37,0:04:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猎巫在现代依然存在 世界各地都有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.29,0:04:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那和我们无关吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.68,0:04:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么傻话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.91,0:04:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.03,0:04:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国外的能力者们随时都可能团结起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.65,0:04:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发起颠覆世界的恐怖袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.93,0:04:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疫苗呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.18,0:04:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然疫苗可以阻止感染者发病
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.36,0:04:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对已经获得能力的人却无能为力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.62,0:04:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就再做个特效药啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.50,0:04:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙坂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.78,0:04:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是个聪明人 但你弟弟似乎并不聪明啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.26,0:04:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,研制新药 需要花费大量的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.53,0:04:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后的世界 不知会变成什么样子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.39,0:04:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管如何 我一定会保护好你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.59,0:04:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.02,0:04:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 先让步未取回有关哥哥的记忆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.09,0:04:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.24,0:04:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.38,0:04:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不就做到了么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.21,0:04:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道你是如何找回记忆的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.45,0:05:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能和某种关键因素有关
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.56,0:05:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可能是偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.21,0:05:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总而言之 我们对此束手无策
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.16,0:05:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…这也太残酷了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.55,0:05:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄妹的回忆 就从今天开始积累吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.45,0:05:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步未
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.00,0:05:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是你们的大哥 隼翼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.64,0:05:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛不太好使 请多关照啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.50,0:05:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问 可以叫你「隼哥哥」吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.66,0:05:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.62,0:05:28.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受得好快！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.20,0:05:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然暂时见不到学校的朋友们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.97,0:05:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你可以交交这些新朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.16,0:05:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们都是能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.03,0:05:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是乙坂步未 请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.56,0:05:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.09,0:05:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多关照哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.30,0:05:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七野 穿个墙给她看看吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.30,0:05:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 可别吓到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.89,0:05:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好厉害的说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.67,0:05:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的娱乐室设备齐全
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.53,0:06:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很多好玩的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.61,0:06:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能听音乐 听哈罗哈罗吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.54,0:06:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.48,0:06:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.99,0:06:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来教你学习
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.21,0:06:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.80,0:06:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.31,0:06:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.32,0:06:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有种被疏远的感觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.46,0:06:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？人都走了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.45,0:06:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次叫文永之役
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.53,0:06:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二次叫弘安之役
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.71,0:06:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.43,0:06:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙古帝国·高丽联军…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.93,0:06:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是妹控吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.29,0:06:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.10,0:06:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…呃 没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.22,0:06:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你急的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.80,0:06:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步未妹妹被大哥给抢走喽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.18,0:06:43.34,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 隼哥哥好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.00,0:06:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有…这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.46,0:06:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就来我这边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.44,0:06:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.40,0:06:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我打两局
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.52,0:06:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.14,0:07:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 来了张好牌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.74,0:07:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立直！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.84,0:07:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.77,0:07:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,役牌两翻 小三元 混一色 对对胡 宝牌三翻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.48,0:07:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庄家三倍满 三万六千
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.73,0:07:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.69,0:07:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 第一次见东一局飞人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.83,0:07:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打得好烂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.70,0:07:17.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是隼翼的弟弟吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.86,0:07:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 再来！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.74,0:07:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.16,0:07:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现新的了 我要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.03,0:07:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次都这么突然
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.30,0:07:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 不能主动寻找 随性得很
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.73,0:07:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果一出现能力者 我就能知道具体信息
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.74,0:07:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那该有多好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.87,0:07:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？发现什么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.15,0:07:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是特殊能力者了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.55,0:07:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来不用淋水啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.29,0:07:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 你要去学生会？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.98,0:07:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.87,0:07:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能一起去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.31,0:07:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呆子 当然不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.93,0:07:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是绝对不能去外面的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.03,0:07:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没这个意识吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.40,0:07:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 对哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.19,0:08:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在 友利在干什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.63,0:08:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想她干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.96,0:08:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请带我去星海学园
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.27,0:08:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古木先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.21,0:08:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.80,0:08:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.08,0:08:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不转弯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.10,0:08:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古木先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.43,0:08:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 熊耳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.17,0:08:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须带你去别的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.47,0:08:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的家人…我的家人有危险
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.78,0:08:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 原来您有家人？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.75,0:08:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直没说 因为有家人就要离开组织
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.94,0:08:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们的规定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.88,0:08:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为你们的OB
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.05,0:08:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都以帮助你们为荣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.88,0:08:56.50,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs58\b0}OB：已毕业的校友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.23,0:08:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别怪我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.60,0:09:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.80,0:09:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.31,0:09:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了 跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.07,0:09:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.55,0:09:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我把人带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.97,0:09:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.93,0:09:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs68\b0\fsp0}Welcome everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.84,0:09:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超能力者 欢迎你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.84,0:09:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外国人么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.00,0:09:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.97,0:09:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.05,0:09:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快放了我的家人！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.34,0:09:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 你得再跑一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.99,0:09:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我出去 等我通知
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.99,0:09:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和说好的不一样啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.80,0:09:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs68\b0\fsp0}You do want to meet your family, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.96,0:09:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还想见你的家人吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.91,0:09:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.96,0:09:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.00,0:09:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.43,0:09:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您应该以您的家人为重
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.65,0:09:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.68,0:10:02.15,note3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,985)}Make sure, he does not die
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.68,0:10:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可别让他死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.27,0:10:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…哪里…？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.44,0:10:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头…好晕…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.30,0:10:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被注射了吐真剂么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.04,0:10:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想让我说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.62,0:10:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你藏起来的超能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.52,0:10:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他们的情报都说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.36,0:10:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼才会说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.74,0:10:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牙都快给打没了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.61,0:10:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我年纪轻轻就全换假牙么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.34,0:11:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我全都…告诉他们了…么…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.10,0:11:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…隼翼…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//----------------------------TXTB----------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.51,0:12:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.24,0:12:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是这个国家的 超能力者的领袖么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.18,0:12:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是日本人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.91,0:12:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.12,0:12:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们国家最强的超能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.08,0:12:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经听熊耳说了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.28,0:12:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊耳？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.73,0:12:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被卷入外国人的恐怖袭击了么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.68,0:12:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊耳呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.89,0:12:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.89,0:12:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是没了指甲和牙齿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.36,0:12:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.50,0:12:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们想要怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.29,0:12:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要乙坂有宇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.31,0:12:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.31,0:12:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们绑架了超能力者 友利奈绪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.73,0:12:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要友利和熊耳 就拿他来换吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.54,0:12:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.66,0:12:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古木会带路
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.62,0:12:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古木先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.66,0:12:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让乙坂有宇一个人来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.05,0:12:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的情报 古木和熊耳告诉我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.86,0:12:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的行动 已经计划了很久
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.47,0:12:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果计划出现偏差
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.34,0:12:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会判断这是利用回溯改变命运的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.79,0:13:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么古木的家人就没命了 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.92,0:13:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此周到…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.78,0:13:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拨号 古木先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.42,0:13:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙坂…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.90,0:13:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古木先生 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.06,0:13:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被威胁了 抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.50,0:13:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.14,0:13:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是从什么时候开始被威胁的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.85,0:13:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我们开始准备建立学园时…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.26,0:13:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难办了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.48,0:13:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果漏了口风 我家人就没命了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.88,0:13:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想过要自杀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.77,0:13:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我放不下我的家人…所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.21,0:13:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才会这样！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.17,0:13:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的判断失误
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.24,0:13:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古木先生不必自责
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.33,0:13:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一定会救出您的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.32,0:13:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.08,0:13:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于来日本了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.42,0:13:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊耳怎么会被抓？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.92,0:13:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古木先生被威胁了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.64,0:14:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.20,0:14:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是有家人的 但是我默许了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.95,0:14:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人竟然从这里下手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.00,0:14:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 让你弟弟回溯到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.96,0:14:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古木先生受威胁之前吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.23,0:14:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古木先生在学园成立前就受威胁了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.62,0:14:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到那时 我们恐怕很难再发展成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.42,0:14:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能整个组织都不存在了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.06,0:14:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风险太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.17,0:14:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 先让弟弟去救回熊耳如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.66,0:14:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古木先生的家人会没命的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.16,0:14:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦有变 敌人就能察觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.40,0:14:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 就派弟弟之外的能力者去…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.10,0:14:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们让有宇一个人去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.76,0:14:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如有闪失 被抓走的所有人都会死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.89,0:14:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,束手无策了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.57,0:14:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让弟弟一个人去 反而会有胜算吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.46,0:14:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.33,0:14:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方也是能力者 正好让弟弟夺走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.38,0:14:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.03,0:14:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以回到现在 重新来过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.15,0:15:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来 敌人也不会察觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.09,0:15:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回溯带来的变化
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.81,0:15:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能赌在有宇身上了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.35,0:15:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真惨…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.03,0:15:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然成了这副模样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.79,0:15:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友利成了人质？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.76,0:15:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿舍的警卫被打倒了好几个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.44,0:15:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人显然是外国的好手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.92,0:15:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定还装备了武器
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.64,0:15:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我独自去见那种人？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.88,0:15:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定能行 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.25,0:15:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先把所有人的能力都夺走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.29,0:15:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他们扔掉武器
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.49,0:15:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得到吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.10,0:15:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要他们没躲起来…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.13,0:15:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们想要你 绝对不会杀你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.57,0:15:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 如果你被抓了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.62,0:15:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是奈绪和熊耳遇到了危险
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.63,0:15:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就使用时光回溯 回现在这个时间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.17,0:15:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时我们再改方案
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.41,0:16:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 千万不要激动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.42,0:16:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦发动崩毁的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.38,0:16:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己也会有生命危险
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.46,0:16:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有宇 听明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.14,0:16:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.99,0:16:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有宇？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.80,0:16:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.37,0:16:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么可能做得到啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.03,0:16:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是一个人就能解决的问题啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.00,0:16:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只会动歪脑筋拿高分
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.43,0:16:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只会当个作弊狂魔啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.07,0:16:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只会为自己着想 是个讨厌的家伙啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.62,0:16:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只想让大家觉得我很好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.04,0:16:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是这么卑鄙！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.84,0:16:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这种人…怎么可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.46,0:16:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.39,0:16:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,专心听我的心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.13,0:16:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管其他事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.84,0:16:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静下来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.36,0:16:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.45,0:16:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我太急了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.00,0:16:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦觉得不妙 就回溯到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.65,0:17:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牢记这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.88,0:17:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还有时间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.50,0:17:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静想想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.49,0:17:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊 靠这张脸就能走桃花运了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.68,0:17:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有必要拼命作弊来添个秀才的高帽吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.05,0:17:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是糟糕的初遇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.33,0:17:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是去搜查
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.36,0:17:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的梦想 是给ZHIEND拍PV
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.38,0:17:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我会一直陪到你恢复为止
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.36,0:17:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我下了决心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.66,0:17:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和步未那时一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.84,0:17:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能等到失去了再后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.68,0:17:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要救出友利
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.52,0:17:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.54,0:17:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好觉悟了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.00,0:17:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.58,0:17:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会跟在你后面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.41,0:17:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.24,0:17:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出事的话 我们会去救你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.66,0:17:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.35,0:17:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是古木先生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.20,0:17:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.07,0:17:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上车吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.26,0:18:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把人带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.22,0:18:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,视野里…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.78,0:18:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有两个人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.57,0:18:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他们都是大人 不是能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.44,0:18:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么便遵守约定 放了你的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.31,0:18:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 拿着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.31,0:18:21.07,note3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,985)}Hey! Take this！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.54,0:18:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是公寓的钥匙 位置写在牌子上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.45,0:18:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…我只能…这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.48,0:18:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行动！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.54,0:18:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没带武器？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.86,0:18:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满意了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.05,0:18:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友利呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.08,0:18:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你正下方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.56,0:19:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人都在地下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.54,0:19:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快放了他们！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.95,0:19:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 快用时光回溯…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.37,0:19:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.37,0:19:25.88,note3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,985)}It's pointless
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.09,0:19:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你没法再用回到过去的超能力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.15,0:19:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然单眼就不能用了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.82,0:19:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果使用崩毁的超能力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.99,0:19:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地下的两人就没救了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.12,0:19:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.06,0:20:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 正在崩毁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.92,0:20:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有用时光回溯吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.96,0:20:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.09,0:20:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.94,0:20:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愣着干嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.54,0:20:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去救人！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.34,0:20:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.71,0:20:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.85,0:20:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望渺茫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.60,0:20:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也必须找找看！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.29,0:20:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈绪！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.97,0:20:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊耳！有宇！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.10,0:20:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼翼！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.79,0:20:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是主犯么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.76,0:20:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目时 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.18,0:20:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.12,0:20:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现弟弟了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.28,0:20:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用念动力躲过了一劫么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.70,0:20:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 他还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.43,0:21:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…有只眼睛被毁了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.31,0:21:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以没能回溯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.54,0:21:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他搬到安全的地方去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.73,0:21:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.60,0:21:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倒是用能力活了下来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.87,0:21:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是另外两人死了可就糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.24,0:21:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里啊…熊耳…奈绪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.14,0:21:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了！两个人都在！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.82,0:21:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.74,0:21:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊耳！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.97,0:21:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊耳 你在哪…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.82,0:21:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回答我！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.00,0:21:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊耳！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.83,0:21:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊耳？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.79,0:21:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼…翼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.06,0:21:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此…为止了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.85,0:21:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊耳 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.60,0:21:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不允许
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.98,0:21:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你必须继续陪在我身边！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.75,0:22:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恕难…从命啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.33,0:22:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 我不允许
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.81,0:22:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊耳 不许就这么走掉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.92,0:22:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不许你离开！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.85,0:22:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼翼…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.04,0:22:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…维尼这个…外号
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.22,0:22:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你…编的吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.35,0:22:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊耳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.65,0:22:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊耳…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.42,0:22:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,900)}熊耳！
