Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.69,0:23:44.34,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}寻获既是结束
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.42,0:23:48.05,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}天空改貌换颜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.11,0:23:51.77,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}群星流转不息
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.83,0:23:55.45,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}待到梦醒之后
